# Sentence Completion App
  Daily journaling app for self-reflection using sentence stems

# Quick Commands
  - `flutter run`              Run on connected device
  - `flutter run -d linux`     Run on Linux desktop
  - `flutter run -d chrome`    Run in browser (web)
  - `flutter test`             Run tests

# Development
  - `flutter pub get`          Install dependencies
  - `dart run build_runner build`  Generate Riverpod code
  - `flutter analyze`          Run static analysis

# Build
  - `flutter build apk`        Build Android APK
  - `flutter build ios`        Build for iOS
  - `flutter build linux`      Build Linux desktop app

